    "Overall, a nimble quantified risk approach prepares organisations to responsibly pursue generative AI's benefits while protecting patients.▪ Ensuring transparency: Ensure transparency of generative AI models by providing clear documentation of the underlying algorithms, data sources and decision-making processes.",
